plot: In an attempt to go to Tampa for an appearance, Khloé, Kourtney and their friend Jonathan get stuck in the middle of the Florida Everglades when their car runs out of gas. And when a nasty storm heads their way, they're forced to spend the night in some strangers' home. Meanwhile, Kourtney thinks she could be pregnant after she realizes she has missed her period and comes down with a bad case of morning sickness.—Guilherme O.
